name: Untitled/Birdman Collection
description:
Another "human" figure with a beak. Is it a self-portrait?Maybe.I have always been obsessed by the shape of beaks, delicate and fragile, pointed and sharp, all at once. They can break easily but also hurt and cause harm. Aren´t we all a bit like that?

Octavio Irving,2019. Charcoal drawing.
